com.aisandbox.cmd.info

Class GameInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aisandbox.cmd.info.GameInfoObject
      • com.aisandbox.cmd.info.GameInfo

  • public class GameInfo
extends GameInfoObject
    All of the filtered read-only information about the current game state. This shouldn't be modified. Modifying it will only hurt yourself. Updated each frame to show the current known information about the world.
